Not a perfectly executed meal this evening but I'm learning with every new step!  Finished the evening with a 4 mile walk for 1 hour 5 minutes burning 614 calories! I am trying to soak up all the country sounds of the night here in Kentucky before I head back to Houston. I miss the sounds of the cicadas, crickets, frogs, and coyotes at night. It's crazy how we take sounds for granted. Guess sometimes its the little things that really matter. ‚ò∫

